[{ "tag": "head", "title": "报到流程", "shareable": true, "contact": true }, { "tag": "p", "text": "\n   由于报到情况多变，本页面仅供参考。如有信息变更，Mr.Hope会尽快对本页进行更新。" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M01/CA/2A/CgpQVFmSgIGAGn9LAAJ7yqVH9Mg1573873/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0" }, { "tag": "h3", "text": "大体流程" }, { "tag": "p", "head": "提前来", "text": "到各学院找接待人员进行登记、领取钥匙", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "到宿舍放置行李", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "报到那天去(本部)到排球场南侧边的同心路/(净月)图书馆门前那找自己学院的摆台处补办手续、领取一卡通", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "在宿舍一楼的自助终端机处修改密码、绑定银行卡、充值。", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "head": "Tips：", "text": "   如果宿舍分配结果还没出来，新生可能暂时被安排到其他宿舍暂时居住，分配具体结果出来后才安排到实际的宿舍去住，会有相关人员进行接待和安排住宿事宜。(可以联系导员了解情况)提前来的萌新们如果到校时间过早或过晚，建议提前联系自己的导员或者学院的学长学姐，说明情况，以便给你建议和帮助。必要的话可以提前和学长学姐联系，请他们给你们带路。" }, { "tag": "h3", "text": "报到当天来" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "(本部)到排球场南边的同心路/(净月)图书馆门前那找自己学院的摆台处进行登记、领取一卡通、宿舍钥匙", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "到宿舍放置行李", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "在宿舍一楼的自助终端机处绑定银行卡、修改密码、充值", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "↓", "align": "center", "style": "font-weight:500;font-size:20px;" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "晚上按时归寝等待导员查寝", "align": "center" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M00/D3/3F/CgpQVFmTzriABTu7AAIudSEDHiY0243843/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0" }, { "tag": "h3", "text": "因故不能按时报到" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   须提供相关证明向录取学院请假，请假时间一般不得超过两周。未请假或逾期不报到者除因不可抗力等正当事由外，视为自动放弃入学资格。" }, { "tag": "h3", "text": "报到(接待)时间" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   2018年8月23日下午13:30—22:00\n   2018年8月24日7:00—22:00" }, { "tag": "h3", "text": "报到(接待)地点" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   本部校区在同心路上(化院、排球场门前对着的那条路)" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/6F/D7/CgpQU1l-wKKACFf_AAC_VnGWuvY5287777/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/23/e9/deb6-fe7a-4b27-be1f-a0a0852be6eb21", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check7.jpg", "desc": "本部摆台地点示意图" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/8a/71/ddd7-b91a-40e2-a8e9-ded31eac4cf704", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check8.jpg", "desc": "本部摆台分布示意图" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/d3/cd/e35d-3d93-4012-b00a-99160802dc0e33", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check10.jpg" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/5d/73/332b-e8e7-4bc2-913d-7b882ab3985245", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check11.jpg" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/20/0f/6b7c-b3c3-4046-968d-8db548ddc8e794", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check12.jpg", "desc": "本部迎新现场" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g3/19/03/63c5-b835-410d-8833-b7fe7ae8637d45", "res": "https://mrhope.top/mpImage/check/check9.jpg", "desc": "本部摆台旁的学生证展板(图片中是Mr.Hope本人哦)" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   (如果当天下雨可能在北苑食堂一楼)" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   净月校区在净月图书馆门前广场" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M01/D3/80/CgpQVFmT0n2ABsINAAZSIYPJymg8963198/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0" }, { "tag": "img", "src": "https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M01/82/B2/wKjmqll93pWAaqvCAAQbHyLV_ko9159655/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0", "desc": "净月摆台地点示意图" }, { "tag": "p", "text": "   (如果下雨可能在一食堂)" }, { "tag": "foot", "author": "沈竞泽、Mr.Hope", "time": "2018/09/18" }]